<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<%- include('./partials/header.ejs') %>
<body>
<%- include('./partials/nav.ejs') %>

<div class="spacerdouble" id="azure"></div>
<section class="boxheader" id="azure">
    <div class="box">
        <h2 class="hidden" style="font-size: 3rem; color: #222323;">Working Towards a Low-Friction Future</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="box">
        <p>A new way to hire and retain freelancers in an ethical and sustainable way with the lowest possible platform fees.
            Utilizing a blockchain solution with low environmental impact, and a proven decade of 24/7 payments.<br /><br /></p>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="splashimage" id="azure">
    <h2 class="abouttitle textcenter abouttitledropdown" id="aboutlist" onclick="toggleDisplay('techabout')">Technology &#10549;</h2>
    <div id="techabout" style="display: none;">
        <div class="box" id="azure">
            <div class="spacer">
            </div>
            <div class="boxheader" id="azure">
                <div class="box">
                    <img src="images/XRPSymbol.png" class="hidden" id="logo">
                </div>
                <div class="box">
                    <h2 class="textcenter fadehide">The XRP Ledger</h2>
                    <p>Using distributed ledger technology, the XRP Ledger allows instant and seamless payments between users.
                        On Volera Platform the Escrow feature allows secure and promised movement of payments between clients and freelancers.<br><br>
                        Learn more about the XRP Ledger at xrpl.org</p>
                </div>
                <div class="box">
                    <h2 class="textcenter fadehide">Escrow Payments</h2>
                    <p>
                        As a native feature of the XRPL funds can be stored in a temporary locked account that the hiring enterprise or oracle retains a key to. Once the job is confirmed to be completed, they send the key to the freelancer to release the escrowed funds.
                        Never share this key with anyone that you don't want to receive the funds.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="box">
                    <h2 class="textcenter fadehide">Send Payments</h2>
                    <p>Send funds directly to other users across the XRPL anytime instantly. Can be used for smaller jobs that do not require the security of escrow.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="box">
                    <h2 class="textcenter fadehide">Wallet</h2>
                    <p>Using the XUMM Wallet you can keep track of your wallet activity, all payments in and out of your account. Total your income for the year, convert to other currencies, self-custody and secure your funds.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="box">
                    <h2 class="textcenter fadehide">Check Balance</h2>
                    <p>Immediately see when funds are deposited into your account, keep track of funds from anywhere with your mobile device.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <a href="https://xrpl.org/xrp-ledger-overview.html"><h4 class="textcenter wave4">Learn More About the XRP Ledger</h4></a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <h2 class="abouttitle abouttitledropdown textcenter" id="aboutlist" onclick="toggleDisplay('userabout')">Users &#10549;</h2>
    <div id="userabout" style="display: none;">
        <div class="boxheader">
            <div class="box">
                <h2 class="fadehide textcenter">Freelancers</h2>
                <p>Showcase your best projects and techinical abilites. Keep your rates the same as any other platform and receive more of the total payout with a flat 5% fee across all jobs. That means more money in your pocket. Work contracts as an individual or as an organization.<br><br></p>
            </div>
            <div class="box">
                <h2 class="fadehide textcenter">Enterprises</h2>
                <p>A frictionless experience so startups and fortune 500 companies alike can easily integrate Volera into their hiring avenues. All for free.<br><br> </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <h2 class="abouttitle abouttitledropdown textcenter" id="aboutlist" onclick="toggleDisplay('walletabout')">Mobile Wallet &#10549;</h2>
    <div id="walletabout" style="display: none;">
        <div class="box" id="azure">
            
            <div class="boxheader">
                <div class="box">
                    <img src="images/xumm-icon.png" id="logo">
                    <p>Required to fully utilize the Volera Platform. XUMM is the integrated wallet on Volera that allows the use of technical aspects of the underlying XRPL technology.<br><br>
                        Instant payments, User IDs, escrow, high-security, and self-custody. </p>
                    <a class="button link textcenter" href="https://xumm.app/">Learn More</a>
                </div>
                <div class="fadehide box" id="image">
                    <img src="images/xummcell.png" id="xumm">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="boxheader wave4">
    <div class="box">
        <h2 style="font-size:3rem; color:azure;">Enterprise Job Listings<br /><br /> Are Free</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="box">
        <p style="color:azure;">Start hiring professionals at launch. Provide opportunites to freelancers across the platform for free. Create your contract, escrow your funds, and hire the right person for the job. For free, and pay as soon as the work is completed.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="wave5 splashimage textcenter" style="height:100vh; justify-content:center; display:flex;">
    <a class="button link textcenter" href="signup">Sign Up</a>
   
    <a class="button link textcenter" href="contact">Contact</a>
</section>

<%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>